      "description": "One-loop massive hexagon with six equal-mass external legs (mass $m_1$) and six equal-mass internal propagators (mass $m_2$). The spanning set of cuts is $\\{\\{z_6\\}\\}$. On this single cut, the diagonal basis has 63 master integrals ($2^6 - 1 = 63$ from all nonempty subsectors of $\\{z_1,...,z_5\\}$ on the cut, plus the sector with no propagator poles giving $2^5 + C(5,1)\\cdot 2^0 + ... = 32$ elements). This is the fully massive case where the prescription works without modification.",
